response.yaml_spec:
reverse_string:
  evals:
    IsString:
      type: str
    ReverseProperty:
      assertion: output[::-1] == input
    LengthInvariant:
      assertion: len(output) == len(input)
  dataset:
  - case:
      id: typical_word
      input: hello
      expected: olleh
  - case:
      id: empty_string
      input: ''
      expected: ''
  - case:
      id: single_character
      input: z
      expected: z
  - case:
      id: palindrome
      input: racecar
      expected: racecar
  - case:
      id: strings_with_spaces
      input: abc def
      expected: fed cba
  - case:
      id: numeric_string
      input: '12345'
      expected: '54321'
  - case:
      id: special_characters
      input: '!@#$%^&*()'
      expected: )(*&^%$#@!
